Dialogue: 0,1:15:34.15,1:15:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,prevailed 93% of the time. Now you ask\Nme to predict what is the likelihood of
Dialogue: 0,1:15:39.60,1:15:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,peace in the near future. You're a dumb\Nquestion.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.12,1:16:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,To be what we are to the fullest\Ncapacity to be that is doing more for
Dialogue: 0,1:16:04.08,1:16:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,world peace than anything else on the\Nplanet.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.48,1:16:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,To be the ultimate capacity of your own\Npotentiality
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.67,1:16:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,that is being a Christ to the world.\NUnderstand
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.28,1:16:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,there's nothing you have to read in a\Nbook by the Christ. I mean that level of
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.60,1:16:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,perfection of consciousness not the\Nperson up historic figure that
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.36,1:16:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,potentiality within yourself\Nto fulfill that that is what's what
Dialogue: 0,1:16:34.96,1:16:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,you're doing for a world peace you know\Nfor which we all thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.12,1:17:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Heat.\NHeat.
